{"tid":1779186,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"中駐美公使再警告 美航母到台灣恰好送解放軍機會武攻","createTime":"2019-12-11T13:28:47.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-11T14:46:42.000Z","uid":28114,"like":12,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"749b7394a3efedb69808c6b4d499a7e6df478590","tid":1779186,"uid":28114,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-11T13:28:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://scd.cn.rfi.fr/sites/chinese.filesrfi/imagecache/rfi_16x9_1024_578/sites/images.rfi.fr/files/aef_image/lnh_0.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fscd.cn.rfi.fr%2Fsites%2Fchinese.filesrfi%2Fimagecache%2Frfi_16x9_1024_578%2Fsites%2Fimages.rfi.fr%2Ffiles%2Faef_image%2Flnh_0.jpg&h=b0f37e4e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n圖為中國遼寧號航空母艦照片 網絡照片<br />\n<br />\n作者：<br />\n小山<br />\n美國總統川普先前簽署《香港人權與民主法案》，導致北京宣布暫停審批美軍艦機訪問香港休整。曾任美國國務院資深顧問的惠頓 (Christian Whiton) 在推特上建議，不讓美國海軍在香港港口停靠，軍艦就使過台灣海峽停靠台灣高雄。對此，中國駐美公使李克新表示，中國的《反國家分裂法》頒布以來一直沒有用過，並要脅 :&ldquo;美軍艦停靠高雄之日，就是解放軍武力統一之時&rdquo;。<br />\n<br />\n據聯合新聞網今天報道指，美顧問稱不讓航母停香港就停高雄， 中國公使說正好趁機武統台灣。<br />\n<br />\n報道稱，中國拒美國航母停靠香港，引發航母停靠台灣的爭議，中國駐美公使李克新甚至說可藉此武統台灣。<br />\n<br />\n據惠頓日前在推特發文表示，北京禁止美國海軍停靠香港，那最簡單的方式就是打通電話給台灣，停靠高雄，然後在回家途中駛過台灣海峽。惠頓被認為與香港反送中抗議人士密切接觸，曾在媒體上公開表示&ldquo;在中美兩國談判的艱難時刻，讓中國亂起來面臨危機，這完全符合美國的利益&rdquo;。<br />\n<br />\n該報道說，駐美公使李克新對於惠頓屢屢叫囂軍艦要停高雄的言論，表示 :&ldquo;你們真要這麼做嗎？那我可能要感謝你&rdquo;、&ldquo;中國的《反國家分裂法》頒布以來一直沒有用過，正好我們可以啟動它試試&rdquo;，並威脅 :&ldquo;美軍艦停靠高雄之日，就是解放軍武力統一之時&rdquo;。<br />\n<br />\n據報，中國駐美外交官此前已經警告，美國軍艦抵高雄之日，就是解放軍武統台灣之時，曾轟動一時。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.rfi.fr/tw/中國/20191210-中國公使再警告-美航母到台灣恰好送解放軍機會武攻\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.rfi.fr%2Ftw%2F%E4%B8%AD%E5%9C%8B%2F20191210-%E4%B8%AD%E5%9C%8B%E5%85%AC%E4%BD%BF%E5%86%8D%E8%AD%A6%E5%91%8A-%E7%BE%8E%E8%88%AA%E6%AF%8D%E5%88%B0%E5%8F%B0%E7%81%A3%E6%81%B0%E5%A5%BD%E9%80%81%E8%A7%A3%E6%94%BE%E8%BB%8D%E6%A9%9F%E6%9C%83%E6%AD%A6%E6%94%BB&d=WPWOQTheSiAT%2FB2p9vAnAK2paxXJRTFpYESBXKIXFX0%3D&h=024f2fa6\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.rfi.fr/tw/中國/20191210-中國公使再警告-美航母到台灣恰好送解放軍機會武攻</a>"},{"pid":"355e31a6a55a7a107aa70301dadd88b7b00e305e","tid":1779186,"uid":28114,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-11T13:30:10.000Z","msg":"我驚流浮山刀手到咗都未見到老解攻台<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"41b6d0c524ef1c642b2f1b3ba97483b0ce2edfd6","tid":1779186,"uid":62270,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-11T13:30:35.000Z","msg":"解放軍攻擊台灣之時，就是中國被美軍滅國之日"},{"pid":"cd9f0aed147bfa431a0118935606e3de2d513950","tid":1779186,"uid":315329,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-11T13:30:43.000Z","msg":"ww3<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"46fb45d644c2942e5287fabc3f16d3df2ccc6add","tid":1779186,"uid":15703,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-11T13:31:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c12b7b971036ea1154bed48bf0a33130d5d5f71f","tid":1779186,"uid":275887,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"cd9f0aed147bfa431a0118935606e3de2d513950","tid":1779186,"uid":315329,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-11T13:30:43.000Z","msg":"ww3<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-11T13:31:46.000Z","msg":"係單方面屌打。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3944e02302d95051fb09bd4f82030f104317bf4f","tid":1779186,"uid":28114,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-11T13:32:18.000Z","